{"tid":2035906,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區議員帶署遭警故意推跌","createTime":"2020-05-26T07:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T07:28:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54cc6f8ef46b0caaa5a63569902d3c009284c011","tid":2035906,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/Z7WBXGC7F6Q7LIPNWJN24MEWRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FZ7WBXGC7F6Q7LIPNWJN24MEWRI%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=192ff386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FZ7WBXGC7F6Q7LIPNWJN24MEWRI%2F&h=a67e11cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/Z7WBXGC7F6Q7LIPNWJN24MEWRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n區議員帶署遭警故意推跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200526/large/1590423715_440c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590423715_440c.gif&h=3ffb45a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區議員葉錦龍前日上街抗惡法時被捕。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前日逾萬人上街反港版國安惡法，人民力量副主席譚得志及兩名區議員被捕，至昨晚仍未獲准保釋。當中兩名區議員葉錦龍及李志宏在灣仔鵝頸橋被捕，暫仍未知涉及甚麼罪名，他們被帶返警署後送院驗傷。沙田區議會副主席黃學禮轉述李志宏稱，他在警署遭警員故意推跌，腳部受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n前日下午5時許，。。。。。。。。容後待他們親自向公眾交代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警避答海港城人叠人<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳景生轟等同改《基本法》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，前日傍晚防暴警衝入尖沙嘴海港城誠品書店外制服巿民，疑似便衣警釀「人叠人」險象，立場新聞女記者更遭男警從後抱住阻採訪，警方昨晚回覆查詢時一直迴避問題，僅指在海港城拘捕10人涉嫌參與未經批准集結。至於女記者被抱開一事，警方稱任何人如認為警方處理事件時受到不合理對待，可向投訴警察課投訴。"},{"pid":"de280287fbff78cb1812a151848dd3795a1f98f4","tid":2035906,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:18:10.000Z","msg":"關於沈教授20點之我見<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035226</a>"},{"pid":"d7f9f1b617113163e511a8e528b9294e4bbde038","tid":2035906,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"狗屋入面打到七彩"}]}